}

See also

AudioPlayer.PlayPaused
SpeechRecognizer.Recognize

Previous directive 
Instructs your client to start playback of a previous audio stream in a playback queue.
Payload field
None
Message example
{
    "directive": {
        "header": {
            "namespace": "PlaybackController",
            "name": "Previous",
