Provides weather forecasts for the week. It is used to display weekly weather on a screen.

Note!
See Screen UI example on how weekly weather is displayed.


Template field



Field name
Type
Field description
Required




bgClipUrl
URLObject
An object containing a URL of the background sound file
Yes


dailyWeatherList[]
object array
An object array containing daily weather
Yes


dailyWeatherList[].date
DateObject
An object containing the date of the day
Yes


dailyWeatherList[].highTemperature
TemperatureCObject
An object containing the highest temperature in the afternoon of the day
Yes


dailyWeatherList[].iconImageCode
StringObject
An object containing weather code for hourly weather
Yes


dailyWeatherList[].iconImageUrl
URLObject
An object containing a URL of the image icon for displaying weather of the day
Yes


dailyWeatherList[].lowTemperature
TemperatureCObject
An object containing the lowest temperature in the morning of the day
Yes


description
StringObject
An object containing a brief explanation that this is weekly weather forecasts
Yes


linkUrl
URLObject
An object containing a link path to the content
No


location
StringObject
An object containing the location
Yes


type
string
A content template delimiter. The value is always "WeeklyWeather".
